  m_text: "Trong qu\xE1 tr\xECnh ch\u01A1i, giao di\u1EC7n s\u1EBD cung c\u1EA5p
    cho b\u1EA1n nh\u1EEFng th\xF4ng tin quan tr\u1ECDng \u0111\u1EC3 \u0111\u1ECBnh
    h\u01B0\u1EDBng v\xE0 ra quy\u1EBFt \u0111\u1ECBnh. L\xE0m quen v\u1EDBi c\xE1c
    khu v\u1EF1c ch\xEDnh tr\xEAn m\xE0n h\xECnh s\u1EBD gi\xFAp b\u1EA1n ph\u1EA3n
    \u1EE9ng nhanh h\u01A1n khi x\u1EED l\xFD t\xECnh hu\u1ED1ng."
